projectGridLines.title: Apps in Etalogue Platform Development
projectGridLines.description:
Description: Etalogue software is new work management platform. This contains various work management Apps for different industries. This project is developing new Apps and enhancing existing Apps on etalogue Work Management Platform.


Skill sets: React JS, Node JS, Python for AI and NOSQL. Good understanding of Data Structures and Algorithms, Agile Project Management. 


This project will have development, testing and operations. 


Expected learning: Deeper understanding of Web, microservices development, Agile project management. 


Specific courses required for project execution:  

MERN Stack courses 

AI Models Courses.

Data Structures and Algorithms

Networking concepts – How internet works end to end, Cyber Security

projectGridLines.title: Bigdata system for Insights, models, recommendations for better practices with AI algorithms /Models for intents prediction for various user inputs and provide information and/or actions.

escription: This project is mainly for processing of the various events and updating in big data platform. Project also includes user interface and related services for visualization of data. For insights bench marking and predication models needs to be developed with AI. 



Skill sets: React JS, Node JS, Python for AI and NOSQL, Graphs, StatisticsThis project will have development, testing and operations. 


Expected learning: Deeper understanding of Web, microservices development, AI models, Statistics, Agile Project Management


Specific courses required for project execution: 

MERN Stack courses 

AI Models Courses.

Mathematics – Statistics 

Data Structures and Algorithms

Networking concepts – How internet works end to end, Cyber Security //Description: User may provide different inputs and may ask for information. Using NLP and context information find the the suitable intents and provide information and/or actions. This project contains identification of data, processing of it and training AI models with the data for intent predications and related actions. 


Skill sets:  Deep learning models, NLP technologies, React JS and Nodejs, Agile Project Management

This project will have development, testing and operations. 



Expected learning: Deeper understanding of AI models with Python, Agile project management

Deep learning with Python
